      • update

        public void update(Observable p_observed)
        this is not a test case, but is used in testing by the other observer test case(s). Note that the update function is normally declared in the view and p_observed is the model. if a View is attached to more than 1 model then the view will need to keep a reference to all the attached models so that it can know which model is being updated (as shown in this test method).
